Excel Dashboard Project
Description:
This project is an interactive Sales Performance Dashboard built in Microsoft Excel to monitor and analyze sales executives’ performance across multiple cities in India. It provides clear visual insights into total sales, target achievement, and areas for improvement, helping managers make informed, data-driven decisions.

## Dataaset used
- <a href="https://github.com/dikshapatidar25/Data--Analysis--Dashboard/blob/main/Dashboard%20%20project12.xlsm"> dataset view </a>

