Tools & Techniques Used :
Microsoft Excel

Pivot Tables & Pivot Charts for data aggregation

Slicers for interactive filtering by city and category

Conditional Formatting for highlighting key metrics

Data Cleaning & Preparation using Excel formulas

 Key Features :
City-based Filters: Select cities like Chennai, Delhi, Mumbai, Nagpur, Patna, Pune, Ranchi, and Surat to view region-specific performance.

Top Sales Executives Table: Displays total sales achieved by leading salespeople.

Target Achievement (%) View: Shows target hit percentage for each executive.

Gap from Target (%) View: Highlights deviation from the set targets.

Dynamic Charts & Visuals:

Bar Chart – Compares total sales by sales executive.

Pie Chart – Shows distribution of target achievement.

Line Chart – Tracks deviation from targets over multiple executives.

